45:29.224 --> 45:33.395
Shh, shh, shh! Quiet study.

45:33.436 --> 45:35.564
Here we go.

45:35.605 --> 45:38.234
When you...

45:38.276 --> 45:41.279
If you need more, I can always

45:41.320 --> 45:43.281
