45:48.869 --> 45:51.580
Thank you. Okay.

45:51.622 --> 45:53.792
Okay, sweetheart.

45:58.714 --> 46:02.301
Okay. Let's talk about
the Continental Congress.

46:02.342 --> 46:05.262
Who can tell me what
that is?/ Excuse me.

46:05.304 --> 46:08.349
Whose paper towels are those?

46:08.391 --> 46:10.351
