46:10.393 --> 46:14.229
Could we maybe put them someplace else?

46:14.271 --> 46:16.106
Mrs. Jensen, they're just...

46:16.148 --> 46:18.942
I know that the kids
need Kleenex, I just

46:18.984 --> 46:22.696
