46:50.601 --> 46:55.231
Okay.

47:48.620 --> 47:49.955
Good to go, little man.

47:49.996 --> 47:53.249
What's going on?
Where's he going?

47:53.290 --> 47:56.335
209, South LaSalle.

48:09.975 --> 48:12.435
Come on,

48:12.477 --> 48:15.523
