48:32.583 --> 48:35.752
Dane Jensen. Wyatt!

48:35.794 --> 48:38.297
Talk to me, babe.

48:38.338 --> 48:40.590
Sure they've got problems at the plant,

48:40.631 --> 48:42.508
is there a manufacturing company
