49:00.527 --> 49:03.156
Cool.

49:03.197 --> 49:06.242
Stir men's blood!

49:08.161 --> 49:11.831
Wyatt? Yeah, listen...
Yeah, I was having lunch

49:11.873 --> 49:16.210
one day in Talladega with
Richard Petty when... yeah,

49:16.252 --> 49:20.382
that Richard Petty.
Anyway, King Richard says to me...

49:20.424 --> 49:22.801
"Make no little plans, Dane,

49:22.843 --> 49:26.305
for they have no magic
to stir the blood."

49:26.347 --> 49:28.097
Well, I'll tell you what it means.

49:28.139 --> 49:30.308
It means if you want to continue

49:30.350 --> 49:34.396
to work a safe comfortable job,
then by all means stay at Rycon.

49:34.438 --> 49:36.440
But if you want a challenging position,

49:36.482 --> 49:38.609
one that will not only
define your career,

49:38.650 --> 49:41.987
but define you as a leader
of men, then this...

49:42.029 --> 49:45.282
This... is your chance!

49:45.324 --> 49:48.495
Well, of course if the money's right.

49:48.536 --> 49:51.456
Forget who you're talking to?

49:56.836 --> 49:59.047
Wyatt?

49:59.089 --> 50:02.050
I'll call you back.

51:11.998 --> 51:16.335
Mmm! Mom, I think our boy's
doing 100% better today.

51:16.377 --> 51:18.880
Some days are good, some days
are bad, but today...

51:18.921 --> 51:20.673
