51:20.715 --> 51:23.302
That's right. So, did they
bring your lunch up for you yet?

51:23.343 --> 51:25.262
Uh, no.
My dad's coming.

51:25.304 --> 51:26.680
Okay.

51:26.722 --> 51:28.015
